      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character and some upcoming maintenance.",
