    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve got to see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled out of the showroom! I have absolutely babied this car, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service interval. It looks and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 43500.0,
