    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner. This beauty has been garage-kept and babied since day one\u2014honestly, it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in flawless shape inside and out, and I\u2019ve made sure it\u2019s stayed in top-notch condition. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so I've priced it to move fast. You really have to see this one in person to believe it\u2014come say hi and take a look!",
      "price": 43500.0,
