    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a superlative example of the E46 chassis. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is managed via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone meticulous preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service, ensuring the mechanical integrity matches its flawless aesthetic. With factory-spec suspension geometry and an uncompromised undercarriage, this M3 offers a pure, analog driving experience that is increasingly rare. A turn-key acquisition for the discerning collector.",
